{
  "stem": "1282.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And today, it's-- everything is known.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's very little that I have intimate information or new information that I could add to it, because remember, I-- I was not working for him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was working within the larger scope of an organization.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that is what got me deported also, eventually.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We'll get to it and I'll explain you about--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, what has happened, I've done this for several months, for seven, six, seven months.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I can't remember the exact timing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But on one occasion-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was several times I had very, very close calls.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're just surrounded-- usually, in Hungarian the name was called [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was where the Germans would surround four corners of a street, OK?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they would surround four outside corners.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And anybody within that, they would gather up and they would have to prove that they are not Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if they were caught, they were condemned.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I have been many times in one of those situations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I escaped them over and over and over and over again, and was very fortunate I escaped them every time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This one time, it was early November in 1944.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was delivering a packet full of papers to-- to one of the buildings, which was close to the Danube.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Most of them were alongside the Danube, because Jewish people owned those buildings which were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] alongside the Danube, very close there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nevertheless, I made an error.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Tired, exhausted.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And instead of coming up with my-- in the fox hole in middle of this courtyard, I came out in front of the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, of course, I tried to get back.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
